"Calls the referenced function previously set by :ref:`set_function "
"<class_FuncRef_method_set_function>` or :ref:`@GDScript.funcref "
"<class_@GDScript_method_funcref>`. Contrarily to :ref:`call_func "
"<class_FuncRef_method_call_func>`, this method does not support a "
"variable number of arguments but expects all parameters to be passed via "
"a single :ref:`Array <class_Array>`."
msgstr ""

